::{{A|VO Side1 ld1 gepard 113.ogg}} '''Gepard:''' As you know, my sister used to be one of the research team leads in the Silvermane Guards Technology Division. Stellarons were her main area of research.
::{{A|VO Side1 ld1 gepard 114.ogg}} '''Gepard:''' But her expertise went far beyond Stellarons. She was and still is well versed in mechanical engineering and other fields.
::{{A|VO Side1 ld1 gepard 115.ogg}} '''Gepard:''' Immediately after her succession, Lady Bronya set her sights on Serval's talents. The supreme guardian wants her to resume her technological research and be a shining light for the revitalization of Belobog.
::{{A|VO Side1 ld1 gepard 116.ogg}} '''Gepard:''' However... you saw her attitude just now. I doubt her meeting with Lady Bronya will change anything &mdash; it'll probably just leave them both feeling dejected.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Maybe she just wants to see the outside world.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I couldn't stand an office job either...
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_101013708-->
::{{A|VO Side1 ld1 gepard 117.ogg}} '''Gepard:''' Mm... I think there's more than one element to it.
::{{A|VO Side1 ld1 gepard 118.ogg}} '''Gepard:''' My intuition tells me this is mostly linked to Madam Cocolia's passing.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I thought they became enemies a long time ago?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_101013711-->
:::{{A|VO Side1 ld1 gepard 119.ogg}} '''Gepard:''' That's true, but...
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_101013713-->
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Sounds like you've got a story to tell. Let's hear it.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_101013713-->
::{{A|VO Side1 ld1 gepard 120.ogg}} '''Gepard:''' *sigh* Never mind, it's just a personal hunch. I've never been good at reading my sister's mind.
::{{A|VO Side1 ld1 gepard 121.ogg}} '''Gepard:''' I can tell the two of you have a close bond. If you get the chance, see if you can persuade her to open up about it.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_101013715-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_101013715-->
::{{A|VO Side1 ld1 gepard 122.ogg}} '''Gepard:''' ...Hand on heart, I wouldn't want to see her sitting behind a desk in Qlipoth Fort and sighing all day either...
::{{A|VO Side1 ld1 gepard 123.ogg}} '''Gepard:''' Belobog is too small a place for a mind as inquisitive as Serval's... Maybe it would be better for her to join you on your journey.
::{{A|VO Side1 ld1 gepard 124.ogg}} '''Gepard:''' *sigh* ...I'll admit, I'm a little worried about how she plans on getting all this across to Lady Bronya.
::{{A|VO Side1 ld1 gepard 125 m.ogg}} {{A|VO Side1 ld1 gepard 125 f.ogg}} '''Gepard:''' (Trailblazer), are you busy? Let's go and wait for her in front of Qlipoth Fort.
