::----
::{{A|VO Side1 ld1 serval 217.ogg}} '''Serval:''' Phew... finally. I think I must have left cadet school with about the same amount...
::{{A|VO Side1 ld1 gepard 150.ogg}} '''Gepard:''' No easy job. Serval, I want to ask you again...
::{{A|VO Side1 ld1 gepard 151.ogg}} '''Gepard:''' Do you... really want to leave Belobog and go with the Trailblazers?
::{{A|VO Side1 ld1 serval 218.ogg}} '''Serval:''' ...Of course! This is a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity &mdash; I can't miss it.
::{{A|VO Side1 ld1 serval 219.ogg}} '''Serval:''' What's wrong, Gepard? Ahh, I see... Can't let go of your dear ol' sister, eh?
::{{A|VO Side1 ld1 gepard 152.ogg}} '''Gepard:''' I... Forget it. I don't want to complicate things for you.
::{{A|VO Side1 ld1 gepard 153.ogg}} '''Gepard:''' But before you leave, I have one last request to make. The Garrison is heading down to the Underworld soon to survey the situation around Boulder Town. Why don't you come with me?
::{{A|VO Side1 ld1 serval 220.ogg}} '''Serval:''' ...Huh? You just said you didn't wanna complicate things for me, and now you're sending me on a mission...
::{{A|VO Side1 ld1 serval 221.ogg}} '''Serval:''' Ahaa~ You just wanna spend as much time as possible with me before I go, right?
::{{A|VO Side1 ld1 gepard 154.ogg}} '''Gepard:''' ...
::{{A|VO Side1 ld1 gepard 155.ogg}} '''Gepard:''' N&mdash;No, it's not that... I've heard there are a lot of old energy hubs in the Underworld, and you're probably the only person in Belobog who knows how to inspect them.
::{{A|VO Side1 ld1 gepard 156.ogg}} '''Gepard:''' Since you're leaving one way or the other, why don't you do the people of the city one last favor before you go?
::{{A|VO Side1 ld1 serval 222.ogg}} '''Serval:''' Even at a time like this, you're still thinking about the people... *sigh* I don't know what to say.
::{{A|VO Side1 ld1 serval 223.ogg}} '''Serval:''' Alright, I'll help you out &mdash; the first and last time the Landau siblings will work together!
::{{A|VO Side1 ld1 gepard 157 m.ogg}} {{A|VO Side1 ld1 gepard 157 f.ogg}} '''Gepard:''' Thanks, sis. (Trailblazer), if you have the time, could you accompany the Garrison?
::{{A|VO Side1 ld1 gepard 158.ogg}} '''Gepard:''' You're Belobog's hero &mdash; I'm sure you must be popular in the Underworld. The Silvermane Guards will face less resistance if you come with us.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Of course, remember to send me a message in advance.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_101013855-->
::{{A|VO Side1 ld1 gepard 159.ogg}} '''Gepard:''' Thanks. I'll contact you when the Guards have finished their preparations.
::{{A|VO Side1 ld1 serval 224.ogg}} '''Serval:''' *sigh* ...I'm tired of packing. Let's leave it here for today. Thanks for your help.
::{{A|VO Side1 ld1 serval 225.ogg}} '''Serval:''' *yawn* I drank all that tea. Why am I getting sleepy?
::----
